      "title": "求角速度比",
      "content": "由 \\(\\omega = \\frac{\\Delta\\theta}{t}\\)，在相同时间内，\\(\\omega_A:\\omega_B = \\Delta\\theta_A:\\Delta\\theta_B = 3:2\\)。",
